NEW MUSIC ALERT🚨 Lady Gaga is proud to be BLACKPINK’s unofficial fifth member! ‘Sour Candy’, the K-Pop group & Gaga’s sassy collab, is out on KKBOX. ⁣
⁣
Listen to Sour Candy on  Lady Gaga’s new album 🔎Chromatica⁣
⁣
Enjoy 7 days of Lady Gaga & BLACKPINK on KKBOX. Sign up now 🎧 https://bit.ly/kkboxsignup ⁣
⁣
🇲🇾 KKBOX celebrates Hari Raya with you! Redeem 14-day music pass with trial code 👉HARIRAYA14 ⁣⁣
Redeem before May 31st. ⁣
